{"tid":468773,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[日經]熱戀期過咗","createTime":"2017-11-14T16:34:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-14T23:01:01.000Z","uid":147789,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"55d674491eaa1f4e780cea902760934db5a7b5ab","tid":468773,"uid":147789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T16:34:23.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打女朋友好冷淡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢中五我year one<br />\n一齊咗2年都有keep 住啱時間就接佢放學之類<br />\n可以話對佢嘅心冇變過<br />\n但係就睇住佢由一開始成日sd 自拍比我<br />\n講下當日發生過咩趣事<br />\n講下變態野佢會笑住咗討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到依家無時無刻都話好多功課又要溫書<br />\n差唔多淨係會問功課<br />\n咁啱出咗街先肯一齊食(同佢住好近 一個西鐵站嘅距離)<br />\n又唔肯出啲遠啲嘅地方(我地住新界西)<br />\n傾電話唔會主動講野<br />\n連講變態野都淨係妖我一下就算<br />\n咁我咪怨下佢我好寂寞之類<br />\n又話我成個怨婦咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我係咪已經冇晒吸引力先會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申已經肯定咗冇<span style=\"color: green;\">帽</span>"},{"pid":"5c34fb3fc2899aa45ac4133cc7c94b2dd26e3cf7","tid":468773,"uid":359,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T16:38:56.000Z","msg":"其實你自己都知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你係到問人，係想有人話你知 <span style=\"color: green;\">叫你唔好諗太多</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8346d316058fa85593781893e8aa45c6e2e59247","tid":468773,"uid":147789,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T16:41:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實你自己都知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你係到問人，係想有人話你知 <span style=\"color: green;\">叫你唔好諗太多</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢唔係雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 只係冷淡<br />\n